# Roadmap - AI Generation
# Shows AI generating roadmap items

Output ../public/docs/roadmap-generate.gif
Output ../public/docs/roadmap-generate.webm

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1000
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 10
Set Framerate 30
Set PlaybackSpeed 1

# Start the application
Type "chloe"
Enter
Sleep 2s

# Switch to Roadmap tab
Type "3"
Sleep 1s

# Generate roadmap with AI
Type "g"
Sleep 5s

# Show the generated items
Sleep 2s
